languages.text: "Какой к гроксу клипер?! Я двадцать два года станцию не покидал! Я в жизни краденного в руках не держал! Не грабил я никаких клиперов!"
"Clipper? What the grox are you on about? I haven't left the station in twenty-two years! I haven't held a single stolen thing in my life! I didn't rob no clippers, all right?"

languages.text: «¿La clíper? ¿Se puede saber qué dices? ¡No he salido de la estación en veintidós años! ¡No he robado nada en roda mi vida! Yo no he asaltado ninguna clíper, ¿te enteras?».

languages.text: 「クリッパー船？何を言ってるんです？22年間、一度もステーションを出たことも、人生で盗みを働いたこともありません！クリッパー船なんて盗むものですか！」
languages.original_text: "Clipper? What the grox are you on about? I haven't left the station in twenty-two years! I haven't held a single stolen thing in my life! I didn't rob no clippers, all right?"

languages.text: "Clipper? Wovon zum Grox sprecht Ihr? Ich habe die Station seit 22 Jahren nicht verlassen! Ich habe in meinem ganzen Leben noch nie etwas gestohlen! Ich habe keinen Clipper ausgeraubt, versteht Ihr?"
languages.original_text: "Clipper? What the grox are you on about? I haven't left the station in twenty-two years! I haven't held a single stolen thing in my life! I didn't rob no clippers, all right?"

languages.text: « Un clipper ? Mais qu'est-ce que vous racontez ? J'ai pas mis les pieds hors de la station depuis vingt-deux ans ! J'ai jamais tenu un seul objet volé entre mes mains de toute ma vie ! J'ai pas pillé de clipper, vous m'entendez ? »
languages.original_text: "Clipper? What the grox are you on about? I haven't left the station in twenty-two years! I haven't held a single stolen thing in my life! I didn't rob no clippers, all right?"

languages.text: "Gemi mi? Bu groks zırvası da ne? Yirmi iki yıldır istasyondan ayrılmadım! Hayatımda çalıntı tek bir şeye bile el bile sürmedim! Gemi falan soymadım ben, tamam mı?"
